## title

### Source (en)

~~~text
Are all the URIs in the RDF resolving to common ontologies?
~~~

### Translation (zh_Hant)

~~~text
RDF 中的所有的 URI 是否皆可解析至通用本體論（ontologies）？
~~~

## text

### Source (en)

~~~text
The FAIR principles ask for the use of FAIR ontologies. It is better when using RDF to make use as much as possible of concepts that are in established and well-maintained ontologies on the internet.
~~~

### Translation (zh_Hant)

~~~text
FAIR 原則要求使用符合 FAIR 的本體（ontologies）。在使用 RDF 時，最好盡可能採用網路上已建立且維護良好的本體中的概念。
~~~
